package.name: super-sub-scripts
package.author: José Ferreira
package.description: A collection of subscripts and superscripts with Latex based naming scheme
package.title: Subscripts and superscripts

manifest.author: José Ferreira
manifest.description: A collection of subscripts and superscripts with Latex based naming scheme
manifest.name: super-sub-scripts
manifest.title: Subscripts and superscripts

packageYml.name: package.yml
packageYml.content:
matches:
  # Math superscripts
  - trigger: ":uint:"
    replace: "ᶴ"

  - trigger: ":u1/4:"
    replace: "¼"

  - trigger: ":u1/2:"
    replace: "½"

  - trigger: ":u3/4:"
    replace: "¾"

  - trigger: ":u1/7:"
    replace: "⅐"

  - trigger: ":u1/9:"
    replace: "⅑"

  - trigger: ":u1/10:"
    replace: "⅒"

  - trigger: ":u1/3:"
    replace: "⅓"

  - trigger: ":u2/3:"
    replace: "⅔"

  - trigger: ":u1/5:"
    replace: "⅕"

  - trigger: ":u2/5:"
    replace: "⅖"

  - trigger: ":u3/5:"
    replace: "⅗"

  - trigger: ":u4/5:"
    replace: "⅘"

  - trigger: ":u1/6:"
    replace: "⅙"

  - trigger: ":u5/6:"
    replace: "⅚"

  - trigger: ":u1/8:"
    replace: "⅛"

  - trigger: ":u3/8:"
    replace: "⅜"

  - trigger: ":u5/8:"
    replace: "⅝"

  - trigger: ":u7/8:"
    replace: "⅞"

  # Math subscripts
  - trigger: ":_0:"
    replace: "₀"

  - trigger: ":_1:"
    replace: "₁"

  - trigger: ":_2:"
    replace: "₂"

  - trigger: ":_3:"
    replace: "₃"

  - trigger: ":_4:"
    replace: "₄"

  - trigger: ":_5:"
    replace: "₅"

  - trigger: ":_6:"
    replace: "₆"

  - trigger: ":_7:"
    replace: "₇"

  - trigger: ":_8:"
    replace: "₈"

  - trigger: ":_9:"
    replace: "₉"

  - trigger: ":_+:"
    replace: "₊"

  - trigger: ":_-:"
    replace: "₋"

  - trigger: ":_=:"
    replace: "₌"

  - trigger: ":_(:"
    replace: "₍"

  - trigger: ":_):"
    replace: "₎"

  # Latin lowercase superscripts
  - trigger: ":ua:"
    replace: "ᵃ"

  - trigger: ":ub:"
    replace: "ᵇ"

  - trigger: ":uc:"
    replace: "ᶜ"

  - trigger: ":ud:"
    replace: "ᵈ"

  - trigger: ":ue:"
    replace: "ᵉ"

  - trigger: ":uf:"
    replace: "ᶠ"

  - trigger: ":ug:"
    replace: "ᵍ"

  - trigger: ":uh:"
    replace: "ʰ"

  - trigger: ":ui:"
    replace: "ⁱ"

  - trigger: ":uj:"
    replace: "ʲ"

  - trigger: ":uk:"
    replace: "ᵏ"

  - trigger: ":ul:"
    replace: "ˡ"

  - trigger: ":um:"
    replace: "ᵐ"

  - trigger: ":un:"
    replace: "ⁿ"

  - trigger: ":uo:"
    replace: "ᵒ"

  - trigger: ":up:"
    replace: "ᵖ"

  - trigger: ":ur:"
    replace: "ʳ"

  - trigger: ":us:"
    replace: "ˢ"

  - trigger: ":ut:"
    replace: "ᵗ"

  - trigger: ":uu:"
    replace: "ᵘ"

  - trigger: ":uv:"
    replace: "ᵛ"

  - trigger: ":uw:"
    replace: "ʷ"

  - trigger: ":ux:"
    replace: "ˣ"

  - trigger: ":uy:"
    replace: "ʸ"

  - trigger: ":uz:"
    replace: "ᶻ"

  # Latin lowercase subscripts
  - trigger: ":_a:"
    replace: "ₐ"

  - trigger: ":_e:"
    replace: "ₑ"

  - trigger: ":_h:"
    replace: "ₕ"

  - trigger: ":_i:"
    replace: "ᵢ"

  - trigger: ":_j:"
    replace: "ⱼ"

  - trigger: ":_k:"
    replace: "ₖ"

  - trigger: ":_l:"
    replace: "ₗ"

  - trigger: ":_m:"
    replace: "ₘ"

  - trigger: ":_n:"
    replace: "ₙ"

  - trigger: ":_o:"
    replace: "ₒ"

  - trigger: ":_p:"
    replace: "ₚ"

  - trigger: ":_r:"
    replace: "ᵣ"

  - trigger: ":_s:"
    replace: "ₛ"

  - trigger: ":_t:"
    replace: "ₜ"

  - trigger: ":_u:"
    replace: "ᵤ"

  - trigger: ":_v:"
    replace: "ᵥ"

  - trigger: ":_x:"
    replace: "ₓ"

  # Latin uppercase superscripts
  - trigger: ":uA:"
    replace: "ᴬ"

  - trigger: ":uB:"
    replace: "ᴮ"

  - trigger: ":uD:"
    replace: "ᴰ"

  - trigger: ":uE:"
    replace: "ᴱ"

  - trigger: ":uG:"
    replace: "ᴳ"

  - trigger: ":uH:"
    replace: "ᴴ"

  - trigger: ":uI:"
    replace: "ᴵ"

  - trigger: ":uJ:"
    replace: "ᴶ"

  - trigger: ":uK:"
    replace: "ᴷ"

  - trigger: ":uL:"
    replace: "ᴸ"

  - trigger: ":uM:"
    replace: "ᴹ"

  - trigger: ":uN:"
    replace: "ᴺ"

  - trigger: ":uO:"
    replace: "ᴼ"

  - trigger: ":uP:"
    replace: "ᴾ"

  - trigger: ":uR:"
    replace: "ᴿ"

  - trigger: ":uT:"
    replace: "ᵀ"

  - trigger: ":uU:"
    replace: "ᵁ"

  - trigger: ":uV:"
    replace: "ⱽ"

  - trigger: ":uW:"
    replace: "ᵂ"

  # Greek superscripts
  - trigger: ":ualpha:"
    replace: "ᵅ"

  - trigger: ":ubeta:"
    replace: "ᵝ"

  - trigger: ":ugamma:"
    replace: "ᵞ"

  - trigger: ":udelta:"
    replace: "ᵟ"

  - trigger: ":uepsilon:"
    replace: "ᵋ"

  - trigger: ":utheta:"
    replace: "ᶿ"

  - trigger: ":uiota:"
    replace: "ᶥ"

  - trigger: ":uphi:"
    replace: "ᶲ"

  - trigger: ":uchi:"
    replace: "ᵡ"

  # Greek subscripts
  - trigger: ":_beta:"
    replace: "ᵦ"

  - trigger: ":_gamma:"
    replace: "ᵧ"

  - trigger: ":_chi:"
    replace: "ᵪ"
